column5: Good to see the kids having a blast
Haven't been out there much, but was planning on maybe one more time this year.  How many inches left bud?
Haven't been out there much, but was planning on maybe one more time this year.  How many inches left bud?   27"+ now and still thickening.
Thanks guys.  I still have time to catch a new species (whitefish).
OMG! A little girl just out fished me for lakers and whities this season!  Anyways good for her. It was a nice catch.

Anyone more in the know then myself want to let me know when the ice is getting 'iffy'? I'd love one more shot at whitefish but don't want to take my life into my own hands.  Oops. Only 6 more days to target whitefish on Simcoe. I'd better get my butt in gear.
Season is closing this weekend. So go get them. As far as ice....plenty of it everywhere...should last easily until season end. Maybe the shoreline could get slushy...  Cheers, Ice Fisherman
